1
00:01:48,786 --> 00:01:50,386
[GASP]
- THAT'S RIGHT!

2
00:01:50,419 --> 00:01:52,919
KAGOME WAS ABDUCTED BY
THE PANTHER TRIBE,

3
00:01:52,952 --> 00:01:55,186
AND IT'S UP TO US TO SAVE HER!

4
00:01:55,219 --> 00:01:57,652
KOUGA AND SESSHOMARU
SHOWED UP

5
00:01:57,686 --> 00:02:01,319
AND ARE ALSO FIGHTING
THE PANTHER TRIBE.

6
00:02:01,352 --> 00:02:04,352
- YOU'LL HAVE TO COME TO OUR
CASTLE IF YOU WANT HER BACK...

7
00:02:04,386 --> 00:02:06,086
IF YOU CAN, THAT IS.

8
00:02:06,119 --> 00:02:10,452
WE'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU,
INUYASHA.

9
00:02:11,986 --> 00:02:14,219
- [GRUNTING]

10
00:02:14,252 --> 00:02:17,452
- SESSHOMARU.

11
00:02:24,619 --> 00:02:27,286
- AAH!

12
00:02:27,952 --> 00:02:29,586
MIROKU!

13
00:02:29,619 --> 00:02:30,652
SANGO!

14
00:02:30,686 --> 00:02:32,652
- SO, YOU'RE ALIVE, SHIPPO.

15
00:02:32,686 --> 00:02:33,652
- HI, MYOGA.

16
00:02:33,686 --> 00:02:34,586
WHERE IS EVERYONE?

17
00:02:34,619 --> 00:02:37,286
- PROBABLY DEEP WITHIN
THE PANTHERS' CASTLE.

18
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:41,519
- HURRY UP AND MOVE OUT OF
THE WAY, OR YOU'LL REGRET IT.

19
00:02:41,552 --> 00:02:44,186
- JUST TRY AND GET PAST US.

20
00:02:44,219 --> 00:02:45,286
- HMPH!

21
00:02:45,319 --> 00:02:47,052
YOU'RE ON!

22
00:02:47,086 --> 00:02:50,486
- HEH HEH HEH!

23
00:02:56,552 --> 00:02:58,786
- YAAH!

24
00:02:58,819 --> 00:03:00,319
WHAT?

25
00:03:02,752 --> 00:03:06,186
- [LAUGHING]
- WHAT IS THIS?

26
00:03:06,219 --> 00:03:07,986
DAMN IT!

27
00:03:16,952 --> 00:03:21,119
- GET OUT OF THE WAY!
- NO CHANCE!

28
00:03:26,186 --> 00:03:27,186
- DIE!

29
00:03:27,219 --> 00:03:31,486
[SCREAMING]

30
00:03:31,952 --> 00:03:34,252
- THEY GOT ROYOKAN!

31
00:03:34,286 --> 00:03:36,619
- WHAT IS THAT?
IS IT LIGHTNING?

32
00:03:36,652 --> 00:03:38,852
- NOT TOO BAD, LITTLE MAN.

33
00:03:38,886 --> 00:03:41,419
HA HA HA!

34
00:03:41,452 --> 00:03:46,886
- HE DOESN'T MOVE QUICKLY,
BUT HIS LIGHTNING IS DEADLY.

35
00:03:48,752 --> 00:03:51,752
- FIREBALL!
HYAH!

36
00:03:54,586 --> 00:03:57,986
AAH!

37
00:04:03,352 --> 00:04:05,819
[PANTING]

38
00:04:13,586 --> 00:04:15,452
TAURON!
- WHAT A SURPRISE.

39
00:04:15,486 --> 00:04:18,586
I THOUGHT YOU WOULD BE WEAKER
THAN YOU WERE BEFORE.

40
00:04:18,619 --> 00:04:20,786
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN BY THAT?

41
00:04:20,819 --> 00:04:22,052
- YOU'RE SHORT AN ARM.

42
00:04:22,086 --> 00:04:27,252
WHO COULD HAVE DONE SUCH A THING
TO THE MIGHTY SESSHOMARU?

43
00:04:27,286 --> 00:04:28,819
[CHUCKLES]

44
00:04:41,586 --> 00:04:44,786
AT LAST, THE CELEBRATIONS
ARE ABOUT TO BEGIN.

45
00:04:44,819 --> 00:04:47,219
WE'LL BE WAITING FOR YOU.

46
00:04:47,252 --> 00:04:50,586
[CHUCKLES]

47
00:04:55,686 --> 00:04:56,919
- WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

48
00:04:56,952 --> 00:04:59,652
NOT HOLDING BACK
ON MY ACCOUNT, ARE YOU?

49
00:04:59,686 --> 00:05:00,986
COME AND GET ME!

50
00:05:01,019 --> 00:05:02,552
- HIS LIGHTNING BOLTS ARE FAST,

51
00:05:02,586 --> 00:05:04,552
BUT THAT'S ALL
HE'S GOT GOING FOR HIM.

52
00:05:04,586 --> 00:05:06,786
ALL RIGHT.

53
00:05:06,819 --> 00:05:08,252
YOU'RE DEAD!

54
00:05:08,286 --> 00:05:12,286
- TOO SLOW!
- OH, NO, I'M NOT!

55
00:05:14,052 --> 00:05:15,386
YOU ARE!

56
00:05:15,419 --> 00:05:19,619
[GROANING]

57
00:05:19,652 --> 00:05:21,419
- HAD ENOUGH?

58
00:05:21,452 --> 00:05:24,086
- RETREAT, PANTHER TRIBE.

59
00:05:24,119 --> 00:05:28,019
[GRUNTING]

60
00:05:28,052 --> 00:05:29,819
- HA HA! SERVES YOU RIGHT.

61
00:05:29,852 --> 00:05:32,186
HOW'S THE BIG GUY
DOING BACK THERE?

62
00:05:32,219 --> 00:05:33,252
- HE'S BREATHING.

63
00:05:33,286 --> 00:05:36,686
- I DON'T THINK HE'S FAINTED.
MORE LIKE HE'S ASLEEP.

64
00:05:36,719 --> 00:05:40,752
- THEN LEAVE HIM.
LET'S GO.

65
00:05:40,786 --> 00:05:44,419
I KNOW KAGOME IS IN THERE.

66
00:05:48,019 --> 00:05:50,686
[LAUGHING]

67
00:05:50,719 --> 00:05:52,986
- I CAN'T TELL
WHICH ONE OF THEM IS REAL.

68
00:05:53,019 --> 00:05:55,886
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING, INUYASHA?!

69
00:05:55,919 --> 00:05:56,819
- SHUT UP!

70
00:05:56,852 --> 00:05:58,752
- LET ME HANDLE THIS!

71
00:05:58,786 --> 00:06:04,386
NOW, BEHOLD AS I DISPEL
THE ILLUSIONS!

72
00:06:05,252 --> 00:06:07,219
- IS THAT THE REAL ONE?

73
00:06:07,252 --> 00:06:08,419
- MM-HMM.

74
00:06:08,452 --> 00:06:12,419
- OH, NOT BAD FOR A LITTLE IMP.
- YOUR TRICKS CAN'T FOOL ME.

75
00:06:12,452 --> 00:06:14,552
DON'T UNDERESTIMATE MY POWER.

76
00:06:14,586 --> 00:06:17,886
- HMPH! NOW THAT I KNOW
WHO I'M DEALING WITH...

77
00:06:17,919 --> 00:06:19,386
AARRGGH!

78
00:06:19,419 --> 00:06:20,186
- HA HA HA!

79
00:06:20,219 --> 00:06:25,919
LET'S CONTINUE THIS
AT THE CASTLE.

80
00:06:25,952 --> 00:06:29,719
- DAMN HER
AND HER STUPID TRICKS.

81
00:06:36,719 --> 00:06:41,586
- THE TIME IS NOW UPON US,
MASTER.

82
00:06:43,686 --> 00:06:46,019
THE MOON IS ALMOST
DIRECTLY OVERHEAD.

83
00:06:46,052 --> 00:06:50,946
IN MOMENTS, THE DOGS
WE DESPISE WILL BE SLAUGHTERED,

84
00:06:50,946 --> 00:06:56,080
AND THE PANTHER TRIBE WILL REIGN
OVER THIS LAND.

85
00:07:06,213 --> 00:07:08,913
- A BARRIER.

86
00:07:13,613 --> 00:07:16,846
- SOON OUR MASTER
WILL BE RESURRECTED.

87
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:20,380
SESSHOMARU, PREPARE TO DIE.

88
00:07:22,513 --> 00:07:26,246
[GROWLING]

89
00:07:38,546 --> 00:07:40,913
[GASP]
- OUR MASTER HAS AWAKENED.

90
00:07:40,946 --> 00:07:49,246
- GIVE ME BLOOD, FLESH...
AND SOUL.

91
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:59,046
- WHAT'S THIS?
- IT'S THE PANTHER TRIBE.

92
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:03,280
- WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?
- KAGOME!

93
00:08:03,313 --> 00:08:07,246
- KOUGA!
- [GRUNTING]

94
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:10,613
- DAMN IT! A BARRIER!

95
00:08:10,646 --> 00:08:11,746
- HA HA HA!

96
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:15,380
AS IF FOOLS LIKE YOU COULD BREAK
THE GREAT ONE'S BARRIER.

97
00:08:15,413 --> 00:08:17,280
- STICK AROUND AND JOIN US
FOR DINNER.

98
00:08:17,313 --> 00:08:20,046
WE'RE HAVING SACRIFICIAL LAMB.

99
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:22,413
[GROWLING]

100
00:08:22,446 --> 00:08:25,680
- FIND YOURSELF ANOTHER MEAL.

101
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:34,080
- MIROKU!

102
00:08:36,113 --> 00:08:37,813
[SCREAMING]

103
00:08:37,846 --> 00:08:40,646
- KAGOME!

104
00:08:41,813 --> 00:08:45,480
- THE TETSUSAIGA IS RED.

105
00:08:45,513 --> 00:08:50,080
[GRUNTING]

106
00:08:58,746 --> 00:09:00,546
- SORRY TO KEEP YOU.

107
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:03,646
- THE MUTT--HE BROKE
OUR MASTER'S BARRIER!

108
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,113
- HOW DARE HE?

109
00:09:05,146 --> 00:09:08,746
- LORD SESSHOMARU!
LORD SESSHOMARU!

110
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:09,780
[PANTING]

111
00:09:09,813 --> 00:09:12,746
I HAVE SEARCHED EVERYWHERE
FOR YOU!

112
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:15,813
INUYASHA HAS SURPRISED ME.

113
00:09:15,846 --> 00:09:17,080
WHEN DID HE BECOME SO POWERFUL

114
00:09:17,113 --> 00:09:20,813
AND LEARN TO WIELD
THE TETSUSAIGA LIKE THAT?

115
00:09:21,713 --> 00:09:24,046
- INUYASHA!
- KAGOME, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

116
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:27,613
- UH-HUH. I JUST KNEW THAT
YOU WOULD COME FOR US.

117
00:09:27,646 --> 00:09:29,580
- [CHUCKLING]
HUH?

118
00:09:29,613 --> 00:09:32,380
- NO NEED TO WORRY ANYMORE,
KAGOME.

119
00:09:32,413 --> 00:09:35,213
- HUH?
- HANDS OFF HER, KOUGA!

120
00:09:35,246 --> 00:09:38,580
- GIVE ME BLOOD!

121
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:42,613
- INUYASHA!
- REST ASSURED, KAGOME.

122
00:09:42,646 --> 00:09:44,880
IT'S GONNA BE EASY TO GET
YOU OUT OF HERE.

123
00:09:44,913 --> 00:09:48,513
- I'M NOT LEAVING
THE OTHERS BEHIND!

124
00:09:57,013 --> 00:09:58,346
- HE'S ATTACKING OUR MASTER!

125
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:01,946
- INUYASHA, THE SACRED JEWEL
SHARDS ARE IN HIS THROAT.

126
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:04,413
- HMPH! GOTCHA.
I'LL GET THEM BACK.

127
00:10:04,446 --> 00:10:06,413
- OK.
ALL RIGHT, PEOPLE.

128
00:10:06,446 --> 00:10:10,780
STICK TOGETHER AND RUN FOR IT!
COME ON, THIS WAY!

129
00:10:10,813 --> 00:10:12,013
[SCREAMING]

130
00:10:12,046 --> 00:10:15,146
- STOP THEM!
DON'T LET THEM ESCAPE!

131
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:17,880
[MURMURING]

132
00:10:17,913 --> 00:10:21,280
- THERE'S NO WAY OUT!
- WE'RE DOOMED!

133
00:10:21,313 --> 00:10:22,713
- WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DOING?

134
00:10:22,746 --> 00:10:25,513
AREN'T WE SUPPOSED
TO BE YOUR LIVE SACRIFICE?

135
00:10:25,546 --> 00:10:28,280
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE NOT
SUPPOSED TO KILL US.

136
00:10:28,313 --> 00:10:29,246
NOW, MOVE.

137
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:32,046
- WOULD YOU LOOK AT HER GO?
- THAT'S OUR GAL!

138
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,146
- ALL RIGHT.
DON'T JUST STAND THERE.

139
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:36,080
CLEAR THE WAY FOR HER.

140
00:10:36,113 --> 00:10:40,180
[SHOUTING]

141
00:10:42,846 --> 00:10:44,213
- [GROANING]

142
00:10:44,246 --> 00:10:47,113
- ARE YOU OK?
MIROKU?

143
00:10:47,146 --> 00:10:50,046
- HUH?
- UP HERE, MIROKU!

144
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,980
- SANGO!

145
00:10:51,013 --> 00:10:54,646
- HELP HAS ARRIVED.
- THEN LET'S GET GOING.

146
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,546
- RIGHT.

147
00:10:57,513 --> 00:10:58,480
HYAH!

148
00:10:58,513 --> 00:11:01,013
- HURRY, PEOPLE!
THIS IS OUR CHANCE!

149
00:11:01,046 --> 00:11:02,646
- THIS WAY!

150
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:06,413
- DIE!

151
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,380
- MASTER!

152
00:11:14,413 --> 00:11:19,813
- GIVE ME BLOOD...AND A SOUL!

153
00:11:19,846 --> 00:11:22,446
- WE WILL.
PLEASE WAIT A LITTLE LONGER.

154
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:25,280
MASTER, I PROMISE THAT I WILL
BRING YOU THE HEAD

155
00:11:25,313 --> 00:11:28,613
OF THE DOG GENERAL'S SON
ON A PLATTER.

156
00:11:28,646 --> 00:11:31,280
- HUH! I DON'T CARE WHO
THIS MASTER OF YOURS IS.

157
00:11:31,313 --> 00:11:35,313
YOU'RE NOT USING HUMAN FLESH
AND BLOOD TO RESURRECT HIM.

158
00:11:35,346 --> 00:11:40,580
- WE WILL, AND YOU SHALL BE
OUR FIRST SACRIFICE.

159
00:11:40,613 --> 00:11:42,113
- YOU MIGHT NOT FEEL THAT WAY

160
00:11:42,146 --> 00:11:45,746
AFTER YOU'VE FELT HOW SHARP
MY BLADE IS.

161
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:54,213
- AHH!

162
00:11:55,780 --> 00:12:00,480
ANOTHER GLORIOUS BATTLE,
MY LORD, AND A VICTORY FOR YOU.

163
00:12:00,513 --> 00:12:02,146
- THERE WAS NO VICTORY.

164
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:04,580
THEY FLED FROM BATTLE,
THAT'S ALL.

165
00:12:04,613 --> 00:12:07,346
I CANNOT USE THIS SWORD.

166
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:09,980
THE TENSAIGA IS
A SWORD OF HEALING.

167
00:12:10,013 --> 00:12:12,746
I CANNOT KILL MY ENEMIES
WITH THIS.

168
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:16,680
I NEED THE OTHER SWORD
THAT FATHER LEFT BEHIND...

169
00:12:16,713 --> 00:12:19,446
THE TETSUSAIGA.

170
00:12:20,013 --> 00:12:21,498
- [GRUNTING]

171
00:12:21,498 --> 00:12:23,398
- WIND SCAR!

172
00:12:23,431 --> 00:12:29,965
- I NEED IT, AND YET I DO NOT
HAVE THE POWER TO WIELD IT.

173
00:12:29,998 --> 00:12:32,431
- [LAUGHING]

174
00:12:32,465 --> 00:12:34,931
- YOU'RE THROUGH!

175
00:12:34,965 --> 00:12:35,898
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

176
00:12:35,931 --> 00:12:39,165
CAN'T YOU USE YOUR SWORD
LIKE THIS?

177
00:12:39,198 --> 00:12:41,298
[CHUCKLING]

178
00:12:41,331 --> 00:12:43,298
-[GASP]

179
00:12:43,331 --> 00:12:47,665
- [SCREAMING]

180
00:12:50,498 --> 00:12:54,698
- [GROANING]

181
00:12:54,731 --> 00:12:57,298
- I TOLD YOU NOT TO INTERRUPT.

182
00:12:57,331 --> 00:12:59,331
- STAY THERE WHERE YOU ARE.

183
00:12:59,365 --> 00:13:02,665
THESE PANTHER DEMONS
BELONG TO ME.

184
00:13:02,698 --> 00:13:03,598
- NOT THIS TIME.

185
00:13:03,631 --> 00:13:06,265
YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO'LL HAVE TO BACK DOWN.

186
00:13:06,298 --> 00:13:09,965
- ENOUGH!

187
00:13:12,331 --> 00:13:15,765
- NO CHANCE!
OUT OF MY WAY!

188
00:13:15,798 --> 00:13:16,931
- AHH!

189
00:13:16,965 --> 00:13:21,465
WHY CAN'T THEY JOIN FORCES
INSTEAD OF FIGHTING EACH OTHER?

190
00:13:23,231 --> 00:13:24,298
- BACK DOWN!

191
00:13:24,331 --> 00:13:27,065
- I DON'T NEED ANY HELP
FROM YOU.

192
00:13:27,098 --> 00:13:28,898
- OH, YEAH?

193
00:13:31,998 --> 00:13:33,865
- ARE THEY BOTH
OUT OF THEIR MINDS?

194
00:13:33,898 --> 00:13:35,998
- IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE
THEY'RE BROTHERS.

195
00:13:36,031 --> 00:13:38,398
- YEAH. WHAT IN THE WORLD
ARE THEY THINKING?

196
00:13:38,431 --> 00:13:41,065
- THE DOG GENERAL'S SONS
ARE FIGHTING EACH OTHER,

197
00:13:41,098 --> 00:13:42,965
WHICH MEANS THAT WE MUST
STAY UNITED.

198
00:13:42,998 --> 00:13:46,765
WE'LL COMBINE OUR POWERS
AND STRIKE THEM ALL AT ONCE.

199
00:13:46,798 --> 00:13:49,165
- ALL RIGHT!
- OH, YEAH!

200
00:13:49,198 --> 00:13:51,131
- RIGHT!

201
00:13:52,131 --> 00:13:55,998
- [GROWLS]
GIVE ME LIFE!

202
00:13:56,031 --> 00:13:58,165
- YES, MASTER.
PLEASE BE PATIENT.

203
00:13:58,198 --> 00:14:02,465
WE SHALL OFFER YOU THEIR SOULS
IN BUT A MOMENT.

204
00:14:04,065 --> 00:14:07,231
- GIVE ME YOUR SOUL!

205
00:14:07,265 --> 00:14:11,198
- AAAH!

206
00:14:11,231 --> 00:14:12,365
- KAURON!

207
00:14:12,398 --> 00:14:16,831
- [SCREAMING]

208
00:14:19,698 --> 00:14:23,965
- HOW COULD HE?
- HMM?

209
00:14:39,331 --> 00:14:45,831
- HE DEVOURED HIS OWN KIN
SO THAT HE COULD REVIVE HIMSELF.

210
00:14:45,865 --> 00:14:52,098
- YOU TWO,
SONS OF THE DOG GENERAL...

211
00:14:52,131 --> 00:14:55,931
YOU'RE NEXT.

212
00:15:10,983 --> 00:15:18,116
- SHONRON, KAURON, SHURON...
IT CAN'T BE.

213
00:15:18,149 --> 00:15:21,449
[SOBBING]

214
00:15:22,283 --> 00:15:28,949
- DOGS! YOU WILL NOW FEEL
THE FULL EXTENT OF MY WRATH!

215
00:15:28,983 --> 00:15:31,383
- TIME TO WAKE UP FROM
YOUR PIPE DREAMS.

216
00:15:31,416 --> 00:15:34,549
MAYBE MY SWORD CAN HELP YOU.

217
00:15:41,316 --> 00:15:43,183
OUT OF MY WAY!

218
00:15:43,216 --> 00:15:46,416
WIND SCAR!

219
00:15:48,616 --> 00:15:49,949
DEAD ON.

220
00:15:49,983 --> 00:15:53,849
- [CHUCKLING]
NO SUCH LUCK.

221
00:15:53,883 --> 00:15:56,449
- YOU'VE GOT THE STRENGTH
TO FIGHT MY OLD MAN,

222
00:15:56,483 --> 00:15:57,583
I'LL GIVE YOU THAT MUCH.

223
00:15:57,616 --> 00:16:00,349
HA! YOU WON'T GET PAST ME,
THOUGH.

224
00:16:00,383 --> 00:16:02,449
- DON'T BE SO SURE, INUYASHA.

225
00:16:02,483 --> 00:16:05,483
HE'S BECOME MORE POWERFUL
THAN RIUKOTSAY.

226
00:16:05,516 --> 00:16:10,949
HE HAS THE POWER OF
THE SACRED JEWEL SHARDS NOW.

227
00:16:11,649 --> 00:16:13,749
- [GRUNTING]

228
00:16:16,549 --> 00:16:20,183
- IT'S THE HUGE PANTHER DEMON!

229
00:16:23,516 --> 00:16:25,849
- LOOK! THE PANTHER KING'S
COME BACK TO LIFE!

230
00:16:25,883 --> 00:16:29,583
- I THOUGHT HE NEEDED
A LIVE SACRIFICE.

231
00:16:29,616 --> 00:16:32,816
- MAYBE HE HAD
SOME FRESH DOG MEAT.

232
00:16:32,849 --> 00:16:35,849
- DON'T SAY THINGS LIKE THAT!

233
00:16:39,949 --> 00:16:42,049
- PERISH.

234
00:16:45,349 --> 00:16:47,716
- LORD SESSHOMARU!

235
00:16:51,649 --> 00:16:52,949
- [CHUCKLING]

236
00:16:52,983 --> 00:16:56,949
YOU SHALL BE MY NEXT VICTIM.

237
00:16:56,983 --> 00:16:59,083
- AARRGGH!

238
00:16:59,116 --> 00:17:01,416
[GRUNTING]

239
00:17:01,449 --> 00:17:06,149
- LORD SESSHOMARU!
MY LORD, WHAT IS IT?

240
00:17:06,183 --> 00:17:14,516
- [GROANING]
CURSE HIM.

241
00:17:23,749 --> 00:17:27,083
HUH? THE TENSAIGA.

242
00:17:30,516 --> 00:17:33,349
YOU WISH TO BE DRAWN?

243
00:17:33,383 --> 00:17:35,416
- AAH!

244
00:17:35,649 --> 00:17:39,149
- FATHER, WHY DID YOU
LEAVE ME THE TENSAIGA?

245
00:17:39,183 --> 00:17:42,549
I STILL DON'T UNDERSTAND.

246
00:17:45,783 --> 00:17:49,583
- [CHUCKLING]

247
00:17:52,249 --> 00:17:54,349
- HUH?

248
00:17:57,116 --> 00:17:59,416
- HUH? WHAT WAS THAT?

249
00:18:01,816 --> 00:18:04,649
- [WHIMPERING]

250
00:18:07,216 --> 00:18:12,249
- YOU CAN'T HARM ME
WITH THAT USELESS SWORD.

251
00:18:12,283 --> 00:18:16,349
ITS BLADE IS FAR TOO DULL.

252
00:18:16,383 --> 00:18:20,883
VANQUISHED!
[GROANS]

253
00:18:20,916 --> 00:18:23,116
MY POWER...

254
00:18:23,149 --> 00:18:25,149
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

255
00:18:25,183 --> 00:18:28,916
I'M LOSING MY POWER...

256
00:18:28,949 --> 00:18:31,549
- HUH?

257
00:18:31,583 --> 00:18:36,416
- I'M LOSING MY POWER.

258
00:18:36,449 --> 00:18:39,849
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE TO ME?

259
00:18:39,883 --> 00:18:43,549
- YOU FINISH HIM OFF
WITH THE TETSUSAIGA.

260
00:18:46,216 --> 00:18:51,049
- GIVE ME MY...SOUL!

261
00:18:51,083 --> 00:18:53,083
- WIND SCAR!

262
00:18:55,516 --> 00:18:58,316
[SCREAMING]

263
00:19:06,049 --> 00:19:09,016
[GURGLING]

264
00:19:15,349 --> 00:19:18,749
- I'M TAKING THESE BACK, THANKS.

265
00:19:20,849 --> 00:19:24,949
- AHH!
- [GROANING]
- HUH?

266
00:19:26,083 --> 00:19:30,416
- TAURON.
- AHH...

267
00:19:30,449 --> 00:19:31,816
- [GASP]

268
00:19:31,849 --> 00:19:33,183
- YOU'RE ALL ALIVE!

269
00:19:33,216 --> 00:19:35,983
- WHAT THE HELL
JUST HAPPENED TO US?

270
00:19:36,016 --> 00:19:38,783
- YEAH. I WAS SURE THAT
THE MASTER HAD KILLED US ALL.

271
00:19:38,816 --> 00:19:40,316
- SOMEONE MUST HAVE SAVED US.

272
00:19:40,349 --> 00:19:43,949
- IT WAS NONE OTHER
THAN LORD SESSHOMARU!

273
00:19:43,983 --> 00:19:45,049
- HUH?

274
00:19:45,083 --> 00:19:46,649
- YOUR OWN MASTER TOOK
YOUR LIVES,

275
00:19:46,683 --> 00:19:50,049
BUT LORD SESSHOMARU USED
HIS SWORD, THE TENSAIGA,

276
00:19:50,083 --> 00:19:52,016
TO BRING YOU BACK TO LIFE.

277
00:19:52,049 --> 00:19:55,416
- HE SAVED US?
- THAT MUTT?

278
00:19:55,449 --> 00:20:00,116
- HOW ABOUT A SHOW OF GRATITUDE?
RIGHT, LORD SESSHOMARU?

279
00:20:00,149 --> 00:20:01,883
WHERE'D HE GO?
HUH?

280
00:20:01,916 --> 00:20:05,749
OH, PLEASE DON'T LEAVE ME
BEHIND AGAIN!

281
00:20:05,783 --> 00:20:07,349
- [GRUNTING]

282
00:20:07,983 --> 00:20:09,783
- SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

283
00:20:09,816 --> 00:20:12,616
WANT TO PICK UP WHERE
WE LEFT OFF?

284
00:20:15,649 --> 00:20:17,583
- HMM.

285
00:20:17,616 --> 00:20:20,516
NO. WE SHALL RETURN TO THE WEST.

286
00:20:20,549 --> 00:20:22,683
- HUH?
- TAURON.

287
00:20:24,183 --> 00:20:25,283
- THIS IS FINISHED.

288
00:20:25,316 --> 00:20:28,283
THERE'S NO REASON FOR US
TO SEEK REVENGE.

289
00:20:28,316 --> 00:20:31,116
YOU CAN TELL SESSHOMARU
I SAID THAT.

290
00:20:31,149 --> 00:20:36,916
- WE'RE NOT EXACTLY A CLOSE-KNIT
FAMILY, IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

291
00:20:36,949 --> 00:20:37,716
- HMM.

292
00:20:37,749 --> 00:20:41,083
JUST TELL HIM NEXT TIME
YOU SEE HIM.

293
00:20:41,116 --> 00:20:43,249
- ALL RIGHT.

294
00:20:45,116 --> 00:20:49,116
- WE ARE FOREVER INDEBTED
TO YOU ALL.

295
00:20:49,149 --> 00:20:50,516
- YOUR VILLAGE WILL BE SAFE NOW

296
00:20:50,549 --> 00:20:53,216
BECAUSE THE PANTHER DEMONS
WON'T BE COMING BACK.

297
00:20:53,249 --> 00:20:54,716
- THANK YOU SO MUCH.

298
00:20:54,749 --> 00:20:58,416
FINALLY, WE CAN LIVE IN PEACE.

299
00:20:58,449 --> 00:21:01,116
- WE SHOULD BE ON OUR WAY NOW.

300
00:21:01,149 --> 00:21:02,516
- [CRYING]

301
00:21:02,549 --> 00:21:07,049
I WANTED TO ASSIST
LORD SESSHOMARU SO BADLY!

302
00:21:07,083 --> 00:21:08,516
- IT'S TOO LATE NOW.

303
00:21:08,549 --> 00:21:12,383
WELL, THERE'S ALWAYS NEXT TIME,
I SUPPOSE.

304
00:21:13,283 --> 00:21:14,683
- WITH GUYS LIKE THAT AROUND,

305
00:21:14,716 --> 00:21:16,783
NO WONDER THE HUMANS ARE SCARED
ALL THE TIME.

306
00:21:16,816 --> 00:21:21,016
- YEAH. THEY GIVE A BAD NAME
TO THE REST OF US DEMONS.

307
00:21:21,049 --> 00:21:22,716
- YES, INDEED.

308
00:21:22,749 --> 00:21:24,016
- YEAH. WHAT'S THE MATTER?

309
00:21:24,049 --> 00:21:27,616
YOU ACTUALLY EXPECT A THANK YOU
FROM THOSE MORTALS?

310
00:21:27,649 --> 00:21:28,649
- YOU AGAIN?

311
00:21:28,683 --> 00:21:31,783
WHY DON'T WE FINISH OFF
THAT LITTLE SCORE OF OURS?

312
00:21:31,816 --> 00:21:33,916
- SURE! THOUGHT YOU'D NEVER ASK.

313
00:21:33,949 --> 00:21:36,316
- YOU SHOULD BE SO LUCKY.

314
00:21:36,349 --> 00:21:38,216
- INUYASHA, SIT!

315
00:21:38,249 --> 00:21:39,116
- UNH!

316
00:21:39,149 --> 00:21:42,149
- JEEZ, WHAT ARE YOU
TRYING TO PROVE?

317
00:21:42,183 --> 00:21:44,449
- OH, MAN!

318
00:21:44,483 --> 00:21:49,149
- [HUMMING]

319
00:21:49,183 --> 00:21:52,316
♪ IN THE MOUNTAINS
IN THE BREEZE ♪

320
00:21:52,349 --> 00:21:55,516
♪ IN THE FOREST
IN MY DREAMS ♪

321
00:21:55,549 --> 00:21:58,783
♪ LORD SESSHOMARU
WHERE ARE YOU? ♪

322
00:21:58,816 --> 00:22:02,483
♪ JAKEN IS SERVING
UNDER YOU, TOO ♪

323
00:22:02,516 --> 00:22:05,683
- RIN.
- LORD SESSHOMARU!

324
00:22:05,716 --> 00:22:08,383
- LET'S BE OFF.
- OH, HURRY UP!

325
00:22:08,416 --> 00:22:10,416
- COMING! AHH!

326
00:22:10,449 --> 00:22:14,516
♪ I WILL WAIT FOR YOU
ON MY OWN ♪

327
00:22:14,549 --> 00:22:19,849
♪ PLEASE RETURN TO ME
WAITING ALL ALONE ♪

328
00:22:26,753 --> 00:22:30,919
[WOMAN SINGING IN JAPANESE]

329
00:22:33,386 --> 00:22:36,119
♪ EVERY HEART ♪

330
00:22:36,153 --> 00:22:40,819
[CONTINUES IN JAPANESE]

331
00:22:47,153 --> 00:22:49,553
♪ EVERY HEART ♪

332
00:22:49,586 --> 00:22:54,519
[CONTINUES IN JAPANESE]

333
00:23:58,661 --> 00:23:59,701
- I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

334
00:23:59,701 --> 00:24:01,267
SANGO'S BEEN PROPOSED TO
BY A LORD!

335
00:24:01,301 --> 00:24:05,267
- HOW CAN SHE FLIRT WITH HIM?
AND RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME, TOO.

336
00:24:05,301 --> 00:24:06,801
- YOU'RE ONE TO TALK.

337
00:24:06,834 --> 00:24:08,134
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO SAY,
SANGO?

338
00:24:08,167 --> 00:24:10,601
HE'S HANDSOME, SINCERE,
AND HE REALLY LOVES YOU.

339
00:24:10,634 --> 00:24:12,501
HE'S THE EXACT OPPOSITE
OF MIROKU.

340
00:24:12,534 --> 00:24:15,801
- NOW, NOW, LET'S NOT START
CRITICIZING PEOPLE.

341
00:24:15,834 --> 00:24:20,267
- WOULD YOU MAKE UP YOUR MIND?
HERE. LET ME DECIDE FOR YOU.

342
00:24:20,301 --> 00:24:23,134
NEXT TIME, "ONLY YOU, SANGO."

343
00:24:23,167 --> 00:24:25,667
- EXCUSE ME, MISS.
WOULD YOU HAVE MY CHILDREN?

344
00:24:25,701 --> 00:24:27,701
- HE'S HOPELESS!

